Please, keep this SVN repo in sync with upstream at: 
https://github.com/opensciencegrid/cvmfs-config-osg

Spec file obtained from packaging/redhat/cvmfs-config-osg.spec inside the repo. Check for changes of .spec between redhat/trunk/cvmfs-config-osg/osg and github.  

To get the upstream:

git clone https://github.com/opensciencegrid/cvmfs-config-osg.git
cd cvmfs-config-osg
git archive v2.0-3 | gzip -7 > cvmfs-config-osg.tar.gz

Or just do:

git clone https://github.com/opensciencegrid/cvmfs-config-osg.git
cd cvmfs-config-osg
git archive v2.0-3 --format=tar.gz --prefix=cvmfs-config-osg-2.0/ -o ~/cvmfs-config-osg-2.0.tar.gz -9

Note, if there is release bump for specific version like above (v2.0-3) set in --prefix only version number for the output tar file
